{"tid":1460419,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[天佑香港] 佔領的原因、正名，行動後續","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T04:00:56.000Z","uid":29899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30e45a58562c36e0fa5533403aa92df7179344b8","tid":1460419,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 我們是現在，我們是未來</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n-佔領的原因，就是要話比呢個政府知：香港人的民意不是「暫緩」、「壽終正寢」就可以敷衍到的事。暴政唔好真係天真到以為示威者「have no stake in the society」，香港人團結上黎，可以隨時就癱瘓到香港的命脈。香港是由香港人組成，唔係任由你班自以為可以隻手遮天的土匪黑社會指指點點，香港既現在以致未來，我地必然會參與其中。而佔領只是香港人眾多的籌碼之一。<br />\n<br />\n-真正係度影響緊香港短期，什至長遠經濟，大家有眼見，係呢個不鳩之所謂, 選擇不回應市民的政府。<br />\n<br />\n-對抗黑警，徹查鄉黑合作，還眾義士公道。由政治引發的事，演變至人道、人權災難&hellip;&hellip;大陸公安都無你地班香港黑警咁仆街阿你班畜牲，我真係屌撚哂你地老母。<br />\n<br />\n-同上，示威者的五大訴求唔係林鄭「唔現實」就可以解決到的事。林鄭辦事不力，成事不足敗事有餘。未解決阿Bitch。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 往後行動的後續/ 對策</span></strong><br />\n<br />\na.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 不割蓆、不分化，團結是香港人的最大力量。</span></strong>幾年前輸，就係因為我地唔夠團結，香港人要爭氣阿。<br />\n<br />\nb. 如果要不定時和理非地估領機場，如何實行，有無辦法可以方便受影響的市民？<br />\n<br />\nc. 如何應對「階段式勝利」，「停一停諗一諗」的偽和理非分子<br />\n<br />\nd. 如何對抗暴政污名化義士及示威者 [War of propaganda]<br />\n<br />\ne. 如何辨鬼，保護同路人"},{"pid":"1fdc4d4b83932728cbe00a5b7967e4d21c78925d","tid":1460419,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8f394047756f53cb4c2599041a1a79387a52b3","tid":1460419,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"[總結] 林鄭：818民陣遊行要人呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ba2b08b941764140eab8aa99465fa5e8124781b","tid":1460419,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"有錯請屌，自己由尋日極嬲，到今日冷靜落黎，先可以寫到少少野。希望幫到香港。<br />\n<br />\n大家真係記住要團結，同埋冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆，不分化，不階段式勝利阿求求你地。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：早幾年有係旺角訓街，第日有人買個包我地食的其中一個香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5993735509c897baebbdad69fff1d321caf1fb65","tid":1460419,"uid":97523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"呢到有少少小弟個人意見<br />\n<br />\n［討論］呢場運動要從長計議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"87781077c35939612c4ebc89c29a532cb9095a63","tid":1460419,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辨鬼就夠 口耳相傳 唔好大聲叫捉鬼</span></span>"},{"pid":"9620a1d438173856b97c613e3feffd60dadbb1ae","tid":1460419,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87781077c35939612c4ebc89c29a532cb9095a63","tid":1460419,"uid":80592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">辨鬼就夠 口耳相傳 唔好大聲叫捉鬼</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"有無前線講下距離黑警幾多米內會係安全範圍？ [假設有鬼準備捉人]"},{"pid":"ff74870e058f6c33b611d16da84a413e65e92907","tid":1460419,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a55de77e924cdf7f619fce0a2728d2573c73f3",